Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.59,0:00:29.31,SR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s something I want to tell you, but it’s too heavy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.31,0:00:35.19,SR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like this, it seems I must break
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.47,0:00:44.38,SR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,There are too many of these indescribable feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.38,0:00:51.22,SR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot deliver them to you, though you are near, the distance is great
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.03,0:01:00.04,SR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Forever only looking up at the blue sky is no good
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.04,0:01:07.27,SR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Spinning around (spinning around)…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.27,0:01:14.68,SR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Unsteadily mustering strength, I want to try diving into your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.68,0:01:21.81,SR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Spinning around (spinning around)…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.21,0:01:31.30,SR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Lightly floating, again today I am alone above the clouds
