Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.33,0:02:03.39,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Iori!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.80,0:02:05.09,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t be mischievous.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.90,0:02:08.08,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Iori…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.05,0:02:11.14,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s been behaving badly lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.14,0:02:14.24,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s hot, hot hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.24,0:02:18.11,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yakumo, isn’t the air\Nconditioner fixed yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.50,0:02:21.53,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,The electrician said\Nhe’d be here about noon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.53,0:02:26.31,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Everyone’s coming over\Nto do homework today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.31,0:02:28.09,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It can’t be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.09,0:02:31.92,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I’ll die in this heat!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.55,0:02:35.98,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,There are people who are out\Neven in this heat, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.66,0:02:41.59,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,They go to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.72,0:02:45.31,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Play sports.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.94,0:02:48.11,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,And lots of other things.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.28,0:02:53.11,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki, you can’t today no matter what?\NNot even for a little while?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.33,0:02:56.28,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so… Okay, then, next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.28,0:02:58.88,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn… Let’s see, who’s next.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.71,0:03:03.05,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyoko-chan, are you free today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.40,0:03:07.23,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so? Okay, then another time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.23,0:03:09.87,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s going on?\NWhat’s happening today?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.48,0:03:12.04,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Next is—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.04,0:03:12.12,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\clip(275,421,412,465)}Next is—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.12,0:03:12.21,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\clip(324,421,412,464)}Next is—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.21,0:03:12.33,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\clip(356,421,412,464)}Next is—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.23,0:03:17.74,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.83,0:03:20.51,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Imadori-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.36,0:03:24.94,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that you, Ichijou?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.94,0:03:25.91,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.91,0:03:27.51,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oww…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.51,0:03:29.43,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m really sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.13,0:03:33.91,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s alright. What’s that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.91,0:03:34.73,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Amateur wrestling?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.21,0:03:36.19,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.97,0:03:39.42,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Amateur wrestling, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.42,0:03:42.18,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be rough in this heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.18,0:03:44.22,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s see, who haven’t I called yet…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.22,0:03:45.91,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,We practice every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.16,0:03:49.54,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Every day? I can’t believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.54,0:03:54.27,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather, for me, summer vacation\Nis time to have fun with girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.67,0:03:56.34,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn’t you be getting a boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.91,0:04:01.55,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, ah, things like that…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.08,0:04:04.61,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really fun doing amateur wrestling?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.61,0:04:07.10,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn’t there anything you should be doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.81,0:04:12.02,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m not good at anything else,\Nand even in wrestling, I’m not so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.35,0:04:16.31,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I’m satisfied. So it’s fun right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.38,0:04:25.87,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sports…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.15,0:04:29.40,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it something you can get so serious about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.91,0:04:33.12,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Eri-chan, here’s some barley tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.58,0:04:34.92,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.43,0:04:39.30,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Miko-chan will be here soon,\Nbut Akira-chan will be a little late.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.59,0:04:43.80,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so? We won’t get\Nanywhere without Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.20,0:04:48.35,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,True. It’s hopeless with us,\Na pair of dummies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.58,0:04:50.31,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,A pair?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.45,0:04:56.04,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second. The only subject I’m poor at is Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.04,0:04:57.94,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s going too far ranking me\Nthe same as you for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.94,0:05:00.84,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Eri-chan, do you\Nunderstand this problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.84,0:05:03.64,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen when people are talking to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.64,0:05:05.88,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, you don’t understand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.88,0:05:08.12,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It can’t be helped.\NI’ll have to do it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.11,0:05:09.87,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.35,0:05:13.37,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, never mind.
