Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.04,0:05:30.10,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.82,0:05:31.83,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.24,0:05:35.65,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s something I want to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.65,0:05:36.84,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.84,0:05:38.10,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ask me! Ask me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.24,0:05:42.82,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever seen a male body?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.20,0:05:47.25,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, no, not that…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.25,0:05:51.03,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, darn. If I’m quiet,\Nit just emerges into my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.18,0:05:53.43,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,That!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.09,0:05:57.21,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of it I end up\Nasking Tenma a stupid question.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.73,0:06:02.39,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,All this because that super pervert\Ndoes something totally ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.94,0:06:08.80,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,But why ask Tenma, who is probably\Nthe densest about such things?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.04,0:06:09.92,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.88,0:06:12.22,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve seen male bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.34,0:06:15.68,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait a minute. What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.78,0:06:18.19,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn’t that ordinary?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.54,0:06:19.40,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Something like that…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.05,0:06:22.66,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That couldn’t mean…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.66,0:06:25.42,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma has had an adult relationship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.42,0:06:27.53,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even I haven’t had one yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.54,0:06:32.37,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Do you mean with Karasuma-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.69,0:06:35.33,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh geez, how did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.73,0:06:37.85,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that’s right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.84,0:06:41.66,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Noooooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.40,0:06:41.91,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord1.5\c&HBC5E09&\b0\fnFrosty's Winterland\fs144\frz41.106\move(794,-64,-80,605)}Shocked
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.40,0:06:42.57,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, just the other day…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.57,0:06:44.97,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Karasuma-kun and I…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.20,0:06:51.58,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What’s the matter, Eri-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.58,0:06:55.31,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Could it be you haven’t seen one?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.83,0:06:57.77,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,And she seems the type\Nthat likes martial arts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.10,0:07:02.19,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.19,0:07:05.44,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you have. It’s only natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.03,0:07:09.70,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I’m mortified. To lose to Tenma…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.38,0:07:13.45,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! Even Tenma wouldn’t\Ndo something like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.55,0:07:16.12,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Like having the mouth blocked?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.79,0:07:19.08,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s just the beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.38,0:07:20.96,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,And him seizing you from behind?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.64,0:07:23.92,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s really a great move, isn’t it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.05,0:07:27.88,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I… I’ve lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.18,0:07:32.56,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,But guys really like\Nthat stuff, don’t they?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.34,0:07:35.60,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.72,0:07:41.48,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Then, if Akira hadn’t\Ncome just then… he would have…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.37,0:07:45.44,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t know what’s going on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.51,0:07:50.24,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, Eri-chan, actually, I wanted\Nto talk over something with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.24,0:07:52.91,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! There’s more?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.91,0:07:54.70,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just ask me anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.04,0:07:58.91,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Er… Um… I think Harima-kun…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.52,0:08:02.83,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,… he likes Miko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.86,0:08:07.86,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I want things to go well between them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.28,0:08:12.42,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I don’t know about these things,\Nso I’d like your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.98,0:08:15.93,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it would be\Ngood for Miko-chan, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.64,0:08:22.89,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was surprised that Harima-kun\Nliked her, but she is cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.48,0:08:29.86,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,But Mikoto…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.14,0:08:33.11,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,… isn’t that cute, is she?
