Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.99,0:09:10.69,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy is very quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.69,0:09:12.38,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it’s this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.69,0:09:15.53,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.82,0:09:17.53,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, part-timer, the ladder.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.53,0:09:18.57,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.52,0:09:21.16,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I’ll leave you to your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.53,0:09:26.33,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Iori! What are you doing here? Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.25,0:09:30.25,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You’ve hurt your leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.88,0:09:32.42,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, lori!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.28,0:09:39.64,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What shall I do? He’s angry,\NI’ve been scolding him a lot lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.40,0:09:43.72,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.22,0:09:46.46,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, a mouse. No?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.89,0:09:49.10,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, you like fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.92,0:09:52.32,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come now, and you get a second one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.59,0:09:58.01,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,No good… all because\NI scolded him too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.48,0:10:00.63,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.51,0:10:24.63,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.77,0:10:32.60,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see… Oh, it’s a thorn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.60,0:10:34.69,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s a thorn behind its leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.27,0:10:38.11,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,He’ll be alright now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.23,0:10:40.51,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.95,0:10:43.41,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah… umm…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.31,0:10:47.65,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like… animals?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.29,0:10:52.17,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well… not especially, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.71,0:10:54.92,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,One day, they suddenly\Nseemed to like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.85,0:11:01.06,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,This house… I remember it somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.30,0:11:15.44,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It… it’s really hot, isn’t it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.08,0:11:17.86,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I open the window a little more?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.25,0:11:19.38,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.42,0:11:26.29,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,But the air conditioner’s broken, so the\Nwindow’s as open as it will ever be.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.26,0:11:33.89,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,This silence is no good.\NI have to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.33,0:11:35.04,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.43,0:11:38.57,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Eri-chan, about this question…
