Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.91,0:11:42.05,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I don’t know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.05,0:11:43.30,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.30,0:11:44.28,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Miko-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.15,0:11:46.53,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Classics?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.53,0:11:49.02,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s see… It must mean this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.45,0:11:51.77,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it does?! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.23,0:11:54.10,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all, that’s nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.89,0:12:07.36,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, say, Miko-chan,\Nabout this problem…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.44,0:12:11.54,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t know that one!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.54,0:12:14.38,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Math? Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.80,0:12:16.67,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is done like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.11,0:12:19.42,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see! You’re good at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.89,0:12:24.01,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You gotta be able to do these\Nif you’re thinking about college.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.68,0:12:32.03,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.03,0:12:34.94,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s no air conditioner, but it’s cool here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.26,0:12:40.30,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Study questions won’t work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.67,0:12:42.43,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to think of a more fun subject!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.68,0:12:45.70,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn’t there… isn’t there anything?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.76,0:12:50.66,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I’m late. The pictures\Nfrom our trip are developed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.94,0:12:53.78,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you! Akira-chan! Show us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.78,0:12:55.92,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s look at the pictures!\NLet’s all look at the pictures!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.61,0:12:58.88,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,See how much fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.09,0:13:03.13,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s this? Imadori\Nreally likes you, Miko-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.62,0:13:04.92,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Woo-woo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.92,0:13:06.05,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have nothing to do with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.46,0:13:08.38,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You couldn’t tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.38,0:13:12.43,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren’t you already dating that bearded delinquent in secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.40,0:13:19.73,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! If you have\Nsomething to say, say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.73,0:13:21.34,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why have you been\Nacting sneaky anyway?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.34,0:13:24.78,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Spreading malicious gossip\Nbehind my back! You coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.78,0:13:26.30,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren’t you ashamed of yourself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.76,0:13:30.83,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?! Then hear me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.28,0:13:34.25,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike you, I don’t\Nmess with just anybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.25,0:13:36.00,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You get all cozy with\Nyour childhood friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.00,0:13:37.92,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,We go to the beach, you get\Npicked up and disappear somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.92,0:13:39.15,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,And, what about Harima-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.15,0:13:42.41,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute! Wait a minute!\NEverything you’re saying is strange!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.41,0:13:46.34,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,In the first place, I saw you and Harima\Nholding hands very friendly-like!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.43,0:13:54.27,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,That? He suddenly appeared, grabbed\Nmy hand and confessed his love!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.69,0:14:00.06,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t stand this! I’m going home!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.36,0:14:01.06,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Eri-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.48,0:14:03.64,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s alright. I’ll see you later, Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.22,0:14:09.41,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Miko-chan, is that true?!\NHarima-kun confessed to Eri-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.66,0:14:16.50,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s true. I thought it best to be quiet\Nabout it and left the scene right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.58,0:14:20.13,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,How can that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.13,0:14:23.30,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Harima-kun was practicing\Nconfessing his love to Miko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.40,0:14:26.34,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,He was working so hard at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.25,0:14:29.59,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,To think he was after both of you…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.09,0:14:32.55,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re the worst, Harima-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.50,0:14:39.58,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re the worst, Harima-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.43,0:14:54.74,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey part-timer, just tell me\Nwhy you’re crying. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.17,0:14:58.21,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No… It’s nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.55,0:15:01.11,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see it’s not nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.11,0:15:04.88,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I… I have no idea\Nwhat’s going on anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.88,0:15:06.54,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it’s adolescence?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.54,0:15:07.88,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it the anguish of adolescence?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.36,0:15:13.95,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m alright. I will do my job precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.65,0:15:16.93,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Refreshments.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.62,0:15:28.40,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm… I don’t know what’s going on,\Nbut please do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.40,0:15:32.73,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll help myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.07,0:15:37.87,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Salty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.42,0:15:40.67,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,So it’s adolescence after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.63,0:15:43.36,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Salty!
