Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.83,0:15:43.88,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord1.2\be1\shad2\3c&HFFFFFF&\fs26\i1\c&HAE690B&\fnFranklin Gothic Demi\fscx65\fscy115\pos(504,139)}www.kickassanime.org
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.16,0:15:52.13,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t mind referring you for\Na part-time job, but why so sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.88,0:15:54.39,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to your last job?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.99,0:15:58.60,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m not fixing air conditioners anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.60,0:15:59.64,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s what I’ve decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.66,0:16:05.75,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever. If you insist,\NI won’t hesitate to refer you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.50,0:16:08.11,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.07,0:16:12.32,note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}Ginjiro Moving Center
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.71,0:16:16.78,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, you guys, let’s get to work!\NHitch up your britches!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.11,0:16:18.05,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.05,0:16:20.22,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why is the beardy here? {Idaho "beard" in dvd subs, "Hige" in wf subs as nickname, changed to "beardy" by me, or should it be "Beardy"?}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.22,0:16:21.75,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.59,0:16:25.72,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I want a lot of cash for dating.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.72,0:16:29.10,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re out of cash, but you want\Nto date? You are truly a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.10,0:16:31.01,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind that, start working!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.40,0:16:35.19,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll work without you telling me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.07,0:16:42.43,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Detachment! I’ll be detached\Nand work earnestly!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.91,0:16:46.40,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s all I can do, now! Go, Kenji!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.58,0:16:50.65,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, newcomer! That’s the spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.00,0:16:53.65,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Carrying that alone is a great feat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.92,0:16:59.08,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m being acknowledged?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.76,0:17:02.22,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hanai’s working hard as usual, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.87,0:17:05.71,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this is training for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.52,0:17:18.38,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn’t s… strain yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.62,0:17:20.74,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Y… You, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.74,0:17:24.23,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You were having a lot of trouble going up those stairs just now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.59,0:17:27.72,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m surprised!\NI’m impressed. Very impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.72,0:17:30.69,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh… What, this is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.69,0:17:32.19,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,E… Easy…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.09,0:17:36.23,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re some workers!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.23,0:17:39.66,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven’t seen anyone carry something\Nlike that alone since Ichi-san, I think?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.18,0:17:41.73,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Ichi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.73,0:17:45.21,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn’t that so, Ichi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.40,0:17:48.00,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.91,0:17:53.21,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Everybody?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.74,0:17:56.55,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Umm… I’m Ichijou!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.55,0:17:58.47,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re in the same class.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.45,0:18:02.18,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Er…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.38,0:18:11.40,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello. This is the first\Ntime we’ve talked, isn’t it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.70,0:18:13.11,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.42,0:18:15.87,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s that amateur wrestling girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.87,0:18:19.20,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Come to think of it,\Nshe was in our class.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.20,0:18:21.37,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn’t know she was\Nworking in the same field.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.84,0:18:23.37,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What, you know each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.37,0:18:27.08,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Having these big brutes bow down\Nto you, you are something, Ichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.27,0:18:29.58,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,No… umm…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.35,0:18:33.80,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, you are too good to be female!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.06,0:18:49.28,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Too good to be female?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.07,0:18:53.48,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I am a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.90,0:18:58.86,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Lifting heavy things is\Njust applying dynamics.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.41,0:19:02.66,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I get tired just like everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.85,0:19:07.85,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.09,0:19:11.19,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Imadori-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.19,0:19:15.13,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You don’t have to strain yourself,\NIchijou. I’ll take care of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.69,0:19:18.88,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn’t a job for a girl. Rest a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.53,0:19:24.70,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah… Thank you, Imadori-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.70,0:19:25.63,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.20,0:19:28.63,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Heave-ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.75,0:19:30.83,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is light.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.21,0:19:39.32,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! I know what to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.67,0:19:44.78,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,If I carry these slowly,\None at a time, I can goof off!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.46,0:19:49.89,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl might have carried\Nall the small boxes at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.89,0:19:53.35,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,With this, I won’t have\Nto do any heavy work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.30,0:20:00.01,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\bord0\c&H040200&\fnVAGRundschriftD\frz15.017\pos(184,83)\frx356\fry348}Salary
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.57,0:20:00.01,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.36,0:20:03.69,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it alright to receive\Nthe same amount as that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.69,0:20:05.47,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a good workout.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.72,0:20:07.74,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Money! Money! A date!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.74,0:20:09.41,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn’t it great?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.41,0:20:15.27,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Really. Right now, I can ask\NIchijou on a date with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.92,0:20:19.76,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.76,0:20:21.21,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.10,0:20:23.70,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What did I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.26,0:20:27.76,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm… It’s my first date!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.76,0:20:29.99,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I look forward to getting to know you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.44,0:20:35.10,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, noooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.10,0:20:39.87,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,My usual bad habit got me\Ninto this outrageous situation…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.11,0:20:48.39,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! An air conditioner and shaved ice\Nhit the spot in summer, doesn’t it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.77,0:20:51.62,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Staying indoors all day\Nis bad for your health.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.05,0:20:53.48,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.29,0:20:57.09,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have all kinds of plans to go out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.09,0:20:59.85,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the fireworks display\Nwith Miko-chan and the gang.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.27,0:21:06.60,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s right… Miko-chan and Eri-chan…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.74,0:21:11.00,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if we’ll be able to go\Nto the fireworks display.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.28,0:21:54.37,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Boys are always chasing after girls
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.37,0:22:00.13,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,All day long they’re thinking of girls
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.13,0:22:04.83,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,But those boys certainly are a little stupid,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.83,0:22:10.30,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,They never seem to understand girls’ feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.75,0:22:14.92,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you really really are a big dummy
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.92,0:22:17.59,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I give you a lesson, Big Dummy?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.59,0:22:20.98,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,So, the most important thing in the world is…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.98,0:22:23.83,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,The thing that absolutely must be…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.83,0:22:28.27,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s definitely “timing”, you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.44,0:22:31.41,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,So, if you wanna say “I love you”,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.41,0:22:34.60,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on a date, or do something…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.28,0:22:40.61,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, kiss, or say goodbye, at any time…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.28,0:22:44.62,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, the most important thing in the world is
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.62,0:22:49.53,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,definitely “timing”, I think, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.53,0:22:50.51,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Or something
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.89,0:23:06.94,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m Sara.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.94,0:23:09.89,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,When I told Yakumo I’d never seen\Na fireworks display in Japan,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.89,0:23:12.39,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,she invited me to go with her.
